- VSCode Version: 1.8.0

I asked [this question on SO](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/41476411/how-to-make-vscode-work-with-global-namespace) but it is more like a feature request for Salsa so I copy it here:

Say I have two files:

```js
// a.js
Abc.foo = function(x) { return x; };

// b.js
Abc.foo(1);
```

The feature request is to enable "Goto Definition [F12]" to jump from `b.js` `Abc.foo()` to `a.js`
